{"tid":2243382,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"「香港解密」公開段崇智個人資料 中大：不排除向私隱公署投訴","createTime":"2020-10-14T16:37:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-15T06:25:38.000Z","uid":240362,"like":248,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"15346f1c62cdfe1a1fc3153d071bfb7e6efd743b","tid":2243382,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T16:37:35.000Z","msg":"網站「香港解密」公開多名教育界人士個人資料，抹黑其為「亂港黃師」，當中包括中文大學校長段崇智，更公開其出生日期、電話號碼和妻子姓名。中大發言人表示，已向網站負責人要求移除資料，不排除向個人資料私隱專員公署投訴。<br />\n<br />\n「香港解密」列出30名所謂「亂港黃師」的個人資料，當中指控段崇智「放棄為人師表責任，目無法紀，公開袒護參與暴動被捕學生」，更列出其出生日期、電話號碼和妻子姓名，惟未知有關內容是否真確。<br />\n<br />\n中大發言人表示，基於《個人資料（私隱）條例》，校方已向「香港解密」網站負責人，要求盡快移除該網站上有關校長段崇智的個人資料，校方不排除向個人資料私隱專員公署作出進一步投訴。<br />\n<br />\n該網站列出2,551人的「起底」資料，分類包括「禍港黑記」、「亂港黃師」、「起底黑手」等。多名《蘋果》記者和職員亦為受害人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201014/4LLFD66TZBDHFIHQGF7IRUZUKU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201014%2F4LLFD66TZBDHFIHQGF7IRUZUKU%2F&d=LQfwTnO421PZAKP%2FvRgyiWg5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=b00b7579\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201014%2F4LLFD66TZBDHFIHQGF7IRUZUKU%2F&h=d4870d41\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201014/4LLFD66TZBDHFIHQGF7IRUZUKU/</a>"},{"pid":"d224af41f5647dd5b5d84451b6ef0a65ec4e8399","tid":2243382,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T16:38:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f176be4a2720e112ee2bab3b8dcb22d1eb417b7","tid":2243382,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d224af41f5647dd5b5d84451b6ef0a65ec4e8399","tid":2243382,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T16:38:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" cl